# Privacy Policy

Last updated: 12/02/2025

## 1. Information We Collect
Queen Bee Kitchen Guide does not collect, store, or share any personal information from its users.

## 2. Data Storage
All data used by the app, including recipes and user preferences, is stored locally on your device. We do not have access to this information.

## 3. Third-Party Services
We do not use any third-party services that collect user data.

## 4. Your Privacy
We are committed to protecting your privacy. Since we do not collect any data, there is no risk of your information being shared, sold, or compromised.

## 5. Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this policy to reflect changes in our practices. Any changes will be posted here.

## 6. Contact Us
If you have any questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at developer.queenbee@gmail.com.
